para_trans: GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: SASB 1125 / P.No.57 / PRASHT-1
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Regulation of transfers of Maharashtra Government employees and in the discharge of government duties.
As per Section 4 (4) and 4 (5) of the Prevention of Delay Act, 2005, the following Ministries
Inter-Departmental transfers of officers of the Joint Secretary cadre are being made and their posting will be done by them.
The name is being done in the section shown in front column-4.
These orders shall come into force with immediate effect.
3. General Administration Department, Government Circular No. Annexure-2022 / Q. 45/18 (R & AW),
Transfer of charge as and when the officers concerned are relieved as mentioned in the 25.08.2022
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
